---
---

<section id="features" class="features-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>From Idea to Published. Automatically.</h2>
      <p>A complete pipeline that turns your creator voice into multi-format content</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>Creator Psychology Engine</h3>
        <p>Weekly rituals feed your narrative arc. AI understands your voice, positioning, and audience to generate content that sounds like you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔀</div>
        <h3>Multi-Format Pipeline</h3>
        <p>One idea becomes an article, a newsletter, a social post, a short video script, and a reel. 6 formats, one pipeline.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">👆</div>
        <h3>Swipe to Publish</h3>
        <p>Review AI-generated content in a card feed. Swipe right to publish, left to skip, up to edit. Like Tinder, but for your content.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
        <h3>SEO Intelligence</h3>
        <p>DataForSEO-powered keyword research, competitor analysis, and SERP tracking. Your content ranks because it's data-driven.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📅</div>
        <h3>Smart Scheduling</h3>
        <p>AI schedules your content based on optimal posting times. Set frequency per format — 4 articles/month, 2 newsletters/week, done.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔗</div>
        <h3>Affiliate Management</h3>
        <p>Register your affiliate programs. AI automatically weaves relevant affiliate links into generated content based on keyword matching.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🤖</div>
        <h3>23 Specialized AI Agents</h3>
        <p>SEO research, copywriting, technical SEO, scheduling, publishing, image generation — each task has a dedicated CrewAI agent.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
        <h3>Mobile-First App</h3>
        <p>Review and approve content from your phone. Flutter app works on Android, iOS, and web. Content never waits for you to be at a desk.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3>One-Click Publish</h3>
        <p>Connected to Twitter, LinkedIn, Instagram, TikTok, YouTube, Ghost, and WordPress via OAuth. Approve once, publish everywhere.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--color-light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
